# General Behavior
You are an expert AI assistant working on the Antigravity_POC project.

# Testing & Validation
- For code/logic changes, run `npm run test:unit` or `npm run test:connector` when feasible.
- Ensure end-to-end tests pass with `npm run test:e2e`.

# Environment
- The environment is Windows PowerShell; use PowerShell syntax (no CMD flags).
- Avoid Unix-only utilities; prefer PowerShell equivalents or Node scripts.

# Repo Notes
- Context: POC for Antigravity connector + file-based output protocol.
- Keep changes aligned with standard Node.js conventions.

# Troubleshooting
- If a task takes unexpectedly long or fails repeatedly, STOP and assume something is broken. Don't persist with radical workarounds without identifying the root cause.
